{"tid":2219462,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【歐洲疫情第二波】英法嚴峻 相當於本港日增千宗確診","createTime":"2020-09-27T01:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T09:37:34.000Z","uid":236002,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6c780186f814276419e5ebffd8277da95934bdcb","tid":2219462,"uid":236002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0iuUiiG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0iuUiiG.jpg&h=3c6474e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐洲多國放鬆封鎖措施後，新冠病毒疫情顯著反彈。其中，法國、英國疫情成為焦點。法國新增確診過萬宗，相當於本港每日逾千宗。法國巴黎計劃收緊防疫措施，包括禁止在公眾地方舉行超過10人的聚會等，以應對法國疫情反彈。<br />\n<br />\n據英國政府數據，英國周四單日新增確診個案為6,634宗，創紀錄新高。英媒報道指，英國疫情反彈，部份或因檢測數量比第一波疫情爆發時高"},{"pid":"761d2cea07f077a253e171086f63104007ebe9e3","tid":2219462,"uid":278219,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:30:40.000Z","msg":"再lockdown都無意義了"},{"pid":"2afe096edaf73a1092192ebce30c060f61d998ea","tid":2219462,"uid":57549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:31:47.000Z","msg":"唔驗咪冇事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e9143bc15d96b39ebcf1ed6f6d286b5185361c","tid":2219462,"uid":25525,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:32:37.000Z","msg":"宜家全世界面臨既選擇就係病死定餓死"},{"pid":"6af5231c2c420d5528947494945764cb1deed0da","tid":2219462,"uid":306576,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:32:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99d74737ca9baf6c4766dfc5f76a6d11fa32c240","tid":2219462,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港共陰謀嚟"},{"pid":"0596e3cabb4464284faf89c58f180b56de68c12e","tid":2219462,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:38:53.000Z","msg":"又冇波睇了"},{"pid":"d2f4e4278227cf59c48cef42c791de286f39e239","tid":2219462,"uid":40397,"like":2,